  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Confusion within TNA over who to support",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "There has been confusion within the TNA regarding which presidential candidate to support in the presidential poll.",
        "The current incumbent for the new presidency is Ranil Wickremesinghe, president and leader of the United Party of India, JVP. The names of leader and opposition MP Anura Kumara Dissanayake and ruling Podujana Peramuna MP Dalus Alagapperuma were proposed.",
        "Meanwhile, some MPs of the Tamil National Federation have insisted on supporting Ranil Wickramasinghe, while another party has also said that they should support Dulles Alagapperuma. At the same time, one of the co-chairmen of the Tamil National Federation has insisted that the vote for the new president should be ignored or a neutral position should be maintained.",
        "Meanwhile, the Parliamentary Committee meeting of the Tamil National Federation was held on Monday, but no final decision was taken. In this case, yesterday evening, the president of the association R. A Parliamentary Committee meeting of the Federation was held at Sampanthan's house and a discussion was held in this regard. Even so, it was not possible to get any official decision regarding the position of the federation till the last hour",
        "Even so, it is revealed through the sources of the party that if the Tamil National Federation is allowed to vote, the votes will be scattered as a secret poll will be held during the presidential election."
      ],
